    <abstract>
      <t>This document records security considerations for the NTRU key
   encapsulation mechanism that is being standardized in ISO/IEC 29192-4
   Amendment 2.  It is intended to help protocol designers and
   implementers decide when NTRU is safe to use, and how to use it
   without creating avoidable security regressions.</t>
